name: Law Offices of Victor E. Hobbs
description: Law Offices of Victor E. Hobbs
overview: Our firm is comprised of experienced attorneys that have represented plaintiffs and consumers from all over the country in many complex and high profile litigation matters. Our teams of attorneys represent many consumers, who have been victimized by fraudulent, abusive, and predatory business and lending practices. Our attorneys have been successful in prosecuting intricate and complex cases against some of the world’s largest corporations, manufacturers and insurance companies. Our main offices are located in Irvine, but we do serve the entire state of California.
